These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, green, white
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of trance is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Color     | green     | azure      | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, sports, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person watching sports movies and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | spy     | superhero      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, rose
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who growsrose and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Flower           | rose | orchid  | daisy   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

