.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, rugby
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Sport   | rugby  | baseball       | cycling       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

