1. the tower house is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the tower house and the spanish##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the tower house and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the colonial house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| House   | tower  | colonial     | palace |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| Transport     | train   | subway   | bike      |

