.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, writer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, prince
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, salsa
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the prince-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Cigar   | prince | siglo   | havana     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

